task.summary: -Crash on showing kernel flash history fixed
-Variables renamed -Device information now declared as private (access over methods) -Report fixed (Kernel Version)
-Layout optimize problems fixed (now Ads and backup/restore options disappears if its turned off or not supported)
-Now can handle unified build source from Motorola MSM8960
-Recovery-Script Manager added (now flash zip over Recovery-Tools :D)
-Added Partition Layouts from Online Nandroid Backup
-Performance improvements creating backups -Some minor UI changes
-Added loki_patch and loki_flash for LG G2
-Better unified builds handling -Stock recoveries and kernels added for nexus devices -New Images Added
-Better version naming from openrecovery-twrp-codename-version to TWRP Version.
-Now recognizing Sony devices if their recovery is stored under /system/bin/recovery.tar (Custom images needs to be downloaded manually

Update [1.9]
-Unified Builds fixed -Onandroid Partition Layouts updated -Spanish translation updated by me -German translation added by me -Better version naming from openrecovery-twrp-codename-version to TWRP Version. -Backups fixed
-Utils-Library updated. -Workspace and project preferences updated for newest Android Studio
-Flash from file browser on some devices fixed
-Better unified builds handling -Style fixes (cards now dark to)
-Now normal reboot after kernel flashing instead of recovery reboot
-Turkish translations fixed and updated by Fathi Firinci
